name: The Boulet Brothers' Dragula
overview: Hosted by The Boulet Brothers, this reality competition show features monster drag artists from around the world competing for a chance to win $100,000 and the title of "Dragula, The World's Next Drag Supermonster". Each week, the competitors are tasked with horror-based makeup, design, and performance challenges meant to test their skills and prove they have what it takes to remain in the competition. For the monsters that fail, grueling mental and physical "Extermination Challenges" await with horrifying and deadly consequences, until only the strongest finalists remain.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: The Boulet Brothers host a competition of drag performers who don't just push the envelope - they chew it up and spit it out. With themes like Zombie and challenges like being buried alive, this ain't your momma's drag competition.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: The second season of the world’s most shocking queer TV series pits ten punk drag queens against one another in a series of extreme challenges to decide which one will snatch the $10,000.00 cash prize, the crown, and the title of DRAGULA – The World’s Next Drag Supermonster.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: Join horror hosts the Boulet Brothers as they welcome eleven drag artists from around the world to compete to win a $25,000.00 grand prize, the crown and the title of Dragula - the World's Next Drag Supermonster.

seasons.name: Season 4
seasons.overview: This season features 11 drag artists competing to be the World's Next Drag Supermonster. The title also comes with a $100,000 cash prize for the queen who snatches the crown and wins the title of DRAGULA.

seasons.name: Season 5
seasons.overview: The Boulet Brothers are on the hunt to find the world’s next drag monster superstar in this brand new, star-studded fifth season of their hit reality competition show. With new competitors, the challenges, special effects makeup, costumes, and performances promise to be truly terrifying and out-of-this-world.

seasons.name: Season 666
seasons.overview: Dubbed ‘Season 666,’ the next chapter of The Boulet Brothers’ Dragula is the most ambitious and terrifying yet, with world-renowned actors and directors joining the judges’ panel, raising the stakes to hellish new heights. Every episode promises spine-chilling, extreme physical feats that will push the cast of drag superstars to confront their darkest fears!

episodes.name: Wickedest Witch
episodes.overview: In this premiere episode, we meet the monster queens competing to snatch the crown and the title of the World’s First Drag Supermonster. Alliances will be formed, throats will be slashed and viewers will be introduced to a reality web competition unlike the world has ever seen. Which queen will rise to the occasion and win the opening challenge, and which queen will meet her death first?

episodes.name: 80's Female Wrestler
episodes.overview: In this second episode, the competing queens crawl one step closer to snatching the crown and the title of Dragula – the claws come out as the fight for survival becomes very real for those finishing in the bottom this episode.

episodes.name: Zombies in Death Valley
episodes.overview: In this episode the remaining queens are taken to Death Valley to face a challenge that will begin to tear at their resolve and relationships with one another. Tensions are high and the contestants face the most shocking elimination yet in their battle for the crown of DRAGULA.

episodes.name: Pretty, Pink, Fishy Drag
episodes.overview: In this episode the remaining queens are challenged to do something more terryfying than being buried alive, or eating pig brains – they have to look pretty! Of course the torture doesn’t end there – tune in and brace yourself for the most controversial execution in the entire series to date.

episodes.name: Trannyshack Club
episodes.overview: In this episode the queens are taken to the legendary club Mother (Trannyshack) in San Francisco to perform for monster drag legends Heklina and Peaches Christ to a song medley created by Alaska Thunderfck, Jer Ber Jones and Dirty Sanchez.The remaining queens face a truly bone chilling extermination challenge, and the final three are finally chosen.

episodes.name: Finale
episodes.overview: In this final episode of the season, the remaining three queens are visited by surprise guests who can either tip the crown in their favor, or drag them to the grave. The finalists will also compete in the final ultimate Floor Show, and one of them will finally be crowned the world’s first drag supermonster!

episodes.name: Reunion
episodes.overview: "The Reunion Show for The Boulet Brothers' Dragula: Search for the World's First Drag Supermonster! Unseen footage and favourite horrors from the first season."

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: The Boulet Brothers host a competition of drag performers who don't just push the envelope - they chew it up and spit it out. With themes like Zombie and challenges like being buried alive, this ain't your momma's drag competition.

episodes.name: Cenobites
episodes.overview: Design an outfit inspired by their own drag style and the Cenobites, a group of sadomasochistic entities physically deformed based on the way the lived and died.

episodes.name: Ghost Town Ghoul
episodes.overview: After last episode’s shocking conclusion, the remaining queens are taken to an abandoned ghost town in the blistering heat to face their second floor show challenge of the season. It all comes down to a midnight showdown at the okurr coral. Warning: there will be blood.

episodes.name: Shock Rock and Metal
episodes.overview: The Search for the World's Next Drag Supermonster continues as the competing queens are split into two teams for their first group challenge, and the queens who were the weakest of the week face a rather permanent extermination.

episodes.name: Sci-Fi Babes
episodes.overview: Set your phasers to stunning and prepare for a journey into outer space! The Brothers take the remaining contestants on a mysterious adventure to the four corners of the galaxy.

episodes.name: Scream Queens
episodes.overview: On this episode of the Boulet Brothers’ Dragula the remaining queens are taken to a remote cabin in the woods where they must survive the night and escape a serial killer who is hunting them down.

episodes.name: Gothic Brides
episodes.overview: It’s time to get sad, lonely and depressed as our queens compete to put on a Gothic Wedding of their dreams.

episodes.name: Welcome to Wasteland (1)
episodes.overview: The remaining four contestants are taken to a post apocalyptic wasteland for a series of challenges that will decide who the final three of the season will be. Stretched over a harrowing weekend in apocalyptic conditions, the queens face three challenges that end in a drag battle unlike anything our viewers have ever seen. Grab your gas masks and your guns and prepare for the end of the world!

episodes.name: Welcome to Wasteland (2)
episodes.overview: The remaining contestants face off in the most shocking battle to date in order to decide who the final three queens of the season will be. Stretched over a harrowing weekend in apocalyptic conditions, the queens face three challenges that end in a drag battle unlike anything our viewers have ever seen. Grab your gas masks and your guns and prepare for the end of the world!

episodes.name: The Last Supper
episodes.overview: With the competition down to the final three, the Boulet Brothers seek the help of the only people they can trust to help them decide who the World’s Next Drag Supermonster will be – the other contestants the finalists have taken out! Join us for our second annual Last Supper as the cast comes together for one final fight in the next step to crowning a star.

episodes.name: Finale
episodes.overview: Interpret and design three outfits with the principals of DRAGULA: Glamour, Filth and Horror.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: The second season of the world’s most shocking queer TV series pits ten punk drag queens against one another in a series of extreme challenges to decide which one will snatch the $10,000.00 cash prize, the crown, and the title of DRAGULA – The World’s Next Drag Supermonster.

episodes.name: The Lesser of Two Evils
episodes.overview: Meet this season's 11 competing drag artists in their quest for the crown. The first extermination commences.

episodes.name: Don't Suck
episodes.overview: The Boulet Brothers challenge the remaining drag artists to craft a vampire visage fit for a queen, and challenge the bottom two queens to a stomach turning extermination challenge.

episodes.name: Drag Monsters of Rock
episodes.overview: The monsters are split into two rock bands and must compete in an arena style show to demolish the opposing band.

episodes.name: The Demon's Blood
episodes.overview: The remaining competitors leave the mansion and go on location for the first time. The pressure pushes people to the breaking point and a mental meltdown threatens to send someone home.

episodes.name: No Throw Aways, Not Recycled
episodes.overview: Fashion meets filth on the runway and competitors must prove they can serve killer looks and deliver memorable interviews on camera. The threat of extermination brings out the fangs in everyone.

episodes.name: The Operating Theatre
episodes.overview: Only 6 competitors remain and it’s going to take surgical precision to survive this weeks challenge. The monsters pose for photographers and editors to see who has the strongest photos. One will win and one will be sent to the morgue.

episodes.name: Le Freak
episodes.overview: Competitors must prove that they have a place in the competition. The Boulet Brothers up the stakes.

episodes.name: Halloween Haunt
episodes.overview: The monsters have to take a classic Halloween costume archetype and elevate the concept with the elements of glamour, filth and/or horror. Also, carve a jack-o-lantern in a way that accessorizes and accentuates the Halloween costume.

episodes.name: Back from the Dead
episodes.overview: The dead are resurrected for one night only to attend the Dragula Season 3 reunion.  Will old wounds and bad blood be infectious?

episodes.name: The Grand Finale
episodes.overview: The strongest monsters deliver their final serving of Filth, Horror, and Glamour. The winner is crowned.

3.name: Season 3
3.overview: Join horror hosts the Boulet Brothers as they welcome eleven drag artists from around the world to compete to win a $25,000.00 grand prize, the crown and the title of Dragula - the World's Next Drag Supermonster.

episodes.name: Horror Icons Reimagined
episodes.overview: The new monsters enter the competition and must reinvent classic Horror icons for their first challenge of the season.

episodes.name: Nosferatu Beach Party
episodes.overview: With one monster exterminated, The Boulet Brothers take the remaining competitors to the beach for the first ever Nosferatu Beach Party.

episodes.name: Weird, Wild, West
episodes.overview: Two monsters have met their end and now the competitors must create looks inspired by the Weird, Wild, West to remain in the competition.

episodes.name: Monsters of Rock
episodes.overview: The Queen Mother of group challenges returns with the annual Monsters of Rock show. Who will be beheaded in the battle of the bands?

episodes.name: Ghostship Glamour
episodes.overview: The monsters must delve into the depths of the dark oceans for a Ghostship Glamour theme and perform a lip-sync to The Boulet Brothers' newest single, "Wicked Love".

episodes.name: Hairy Monsters
episodes.overview: The competitors are challenged with creating their hairiest creatures yet for this week's theme; one monster will be a cut above the rest and another will get the chop in a truly squirm-worthy extermination.

episodes.name: Exorsisters
episodes.overview: The monsters face their toughest challenge yet - starring in their own horror movie.

episodes.name: Killer Clowns
episodes.overview: With one challenge left to determine the season's finalist, the stakes have never been higher; the monsters must create looks based on the theme of Killer Clowns.

episodes.name: The Last Supper!
episodes.overview: The exterminated monsters return to the land of the living to air their grievances and join The Boulet Brothers' in the Dragula Season 4 reunion.

episodes.name: Grand Finale
episodes.overview: Only the strongest competitors remain as the finalists compete in a grand finale of epic proportions, proving who will be crowned "Dragula, The World's Next Drag Supermonster".

4.name: Season 4
4.overview: This season features 11 drag artists competing to be the World's Next Drag Supermonster. The title also comes with a $100,000 cash prize for the queen who snatches the crown and wins the title of DRAGULA.

episodes.name: Terror In The Woods
episodes.overview: The Boulet Brothers welcome an all new cast to a brand new set and an all new set of challenges.

episodes.name: Children of the Can
episodes.overview: After the first extermination, the cast comes together to face the next challenge and an unexpected surprise.

episodes.name: Ghosts of the Gatehouse
episodes.overview: After the shocking events of the previous episode, the cast begins to draw battle lines with one another and choose teams.

episodes.name: Gods of Death (Part 1)
episodes.overview: The cast must fight independently for their spot on the next challenge, and a surprise elimination leaves them all shocked.

episodes.name: It Came From Beyond
episodes.overview: The mansion (and the entire cast) are beamed to outer space.

episodes.name: Ultraviolet Umbras
episodes.overview: The cast must create costumes, looks, and makeup treatments using spectrums of light as a base.

episodes.name: Humungous Horrors
episodes.overview: The challenge that decides the top three of the season has the entire remaining cast feeling uneasy.

episodes.name: The Last Supper
episodes.overview: The entire cast reunites to revisit the season, address unfinished business, and put forth their vote on who they think should win.

episodes.name: The Grand Finale
episodes.overview: The season Grand Finale! After a harrowing season of incredible challenges, the Boulet Brothers will crown the world's next Drag Supermonster.

episodes.name: Welcome to Hell!
episodes.overview: Welcome to Hollywood: new challenges & exterminations await!

episodes.name: Killer Dolls
episodes.overview: Cast meets guest judges Jennifer Tilly and Don Mancini.

episodes.name: Holiday of Horrors
episodes.overview: Drag stars craft holiday horror looks.

episodes.name: The Ghost Train
episodes.overview: The remaining competitors head to a haunted railroad for a ride on the Ghost Train.

episodes.name: Dragula The Musical
episodes.overview: Dragula the musical!

episodes.name: Monochrome Monster
episodes.overview: Attack of the Monochrome Monsters.
